description: Tension reigns supreme all over the headquarters of Prince Dezerad's Secret Legion. Not even the kitchen staff is immune from the sharp anxiety and edginess pervading the atmosphere. Ty Russell and Bo Summers decide they're not gonna take any more shit from bossy Chance Caldwell so they subdue the head cook and force feed him their cocks, stuffing them down his throat and up his ass. Squealing like a skewered pig, Chance can do nothing but succumb to the sexual assault.

title: The Abduction Series, Part II - The Conflict, Scene #01
